snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's marriage to be made into a documentary series
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard’s troubled marriage and divorce are set to become the subject of a new documentary series for Discovery titled 'Johnny vs Amber'.
#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard
